        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>One of the key strengths of the Malbon Golf Performance Collection is its versatility. While each piece is designed with golf in mind, the sleek designs and high-quality materials make them suitable for a variety of occasions. Whether you're heading to the clubhouse, or enjoying a casual evening out, the pieces from this collection transition seamlessly from the course to everyday life.</p><h2><strong>Sustainable Practices and Quality Craftsmanship</strong></h2><p>Malbon Golf is committed to sustainability and ethical manufacturing practices. The Performance Collection is a testament to this commitment, with each piece crafted using environmentally friendly methods and materials. The durability of the fabrics ensures that these garments are long-lasting, reducing the need for frequent replacements and contributing to a more sustainable wardrobe.</p>"
